  "response": "In Bangalore, there are several spas where male therapists might offer massages to women. However, policies regarding male therapists providing massages to female clients can vary greatly between establishments due to local cultural norms and regulations. It's best to contact the spa directly to inquire about their services and booking policies.\n\nSome well-known spa chains in Bangalore that may offer such services include:\n\n1. **O2 Spa** - They have various locations across Bangalore and provide a wide range of spa services.\n\n2. **Four Fountains De-Stress Spa** - Known for their therapeutic massages and wellness treatments.\n\n3. **The Palms Spa** - Offers luxury spa treatments and might have male therapists available.\n\n4. **Kerala Ayurveda** - Provides authentic Ayurvedic treatments and massages.\n\nWhen reaching out to these spas, you can specifically ask about the availability of male therapists for female clients to ensure they meet your preferences. Always ensure that the spa you choose is reputable and follows necessary health and safety standards.",
